    <Folder><name>1. Forest Area</name><description>Draw polygons over forested canopy (Add &gt; Polygon, apply this folder's style).</description></Folder>
    <Folder><name>2. Water Bodies / River</name><description>Trace lakes/ponds as polygons, rivers as paths.</description></Folder>
    <Folder><name>3. Roads &amp; Tracks</name><description>Trace as paths (Add &gt; Path).</description></Folder>
    <Folder><name>4. Streams / Nullahs</name><description>Trace seasonal watercourses as paths.</description></Folder>
    <Folder><name>5. Settlements / Houses</name><description>Drop placemarks on visible structures.</description></Folder>
    <Folder><name>6. Points of Interest</name><description>Temples, wells, schools, survey markers, etc.</description></Folder>
    <Folder><name>7. Terrain Notes</name><description>Optional: peaks, ridges, elevation labels (enable 3D terrain to see relief).</description></Folder>
